STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
Darryl A. ROUNDTREE, Craig L. Owens, Jr., Tyerice D. Peace and Maurice E. Peace, Defendants. M-1429/1430 September Term 2017
079961 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 6, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion to strike portions of the American Civil Liberties Union of New Jersey's amicus curiae brief (M-1429) is denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a supplemental reply brief (M-1430) is granted.
